Southern Cross Tourist Co. of Mauritus Returns to Profit During Full-Year

-- B y   K a m l e s h   B h u c k o r y
-- 
2011-03-28T06:02:12Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-28/southern-cross-tourist-co-of-mauritus-returns-to-profit-during-full-year.html
Southern Cross Tourist Co. posted
net income of 35 million rupees ($1.2 million) for the 12 months
through December, up from a loss of 132 million rupees a year
earlier.  The company commented in a stock exchange statement today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
